import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
from scipy.stats import linregress
import matplotlib as mpl
from matplotlib.colors import LightSource
mpl.rc('font', family='sans-serif') 
mpl.rc('font', serif='Arial')
mpl.rc('pdf', fonttype=42)
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

% matplotlib inline
## Plot D50, D84, D90 as a function of distance inland

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8.5,11))

# D50 plot
ax1 = plt.subplot(4,1,1)
plt.plot(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'],sand_a['D50 Phi'],'k.')
mask = ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'])) & ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['D50 Phi']))
d50_regress = linregress(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'][mask],sand_a['D50 Phi'][mask])
x = np.linspace(0,400,401)
ax1.plot(x, d50_regress[0]*x + d50_regress[1],'k--')
ax1.annotate('$r^2 = %.2f$' %d50_regress[2]**2, xy=(0.85,0.9), xycoords="axes fraction")
ax1.set_xlim(0,400)
ax1.set_ylabel('D50 grainsize $\phi$')
plt.grid()
ax1_mm = ax1.twinx()
ax1_mm.set_ylim(phi2mm(ax1.get_ylim()[0]),phi2mm(ax1.get_ylim()[1]))
ax1_mm.set_ylabel('D50 grainsize mm')
plt.gca().invert_xaxis()

# D84 plot
ax2 = plt.subplot(4,1,2)
plt.plot(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'],sand_a['D84 Phi'],'k.')
mask = ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'])) & ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['D84 Phi']))
d84_regress = linregress(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'][mask],sand_a['D84 Phi'][mask])
ax2.plot(x, d84_regress[0]*x + d84_regress[1],'k--')
ax2.annotate('$r^2 = %.2f$' %d84_regress[2]**2, xy=(0.85,0.9), xycoords="axes fraction")
ax2.set_xlim(0,400)
ax2.set_ylabel('D84 grainsize $\phi$')
plt.grid()
ax2_mm = ax2.twinx()
ax2_mm.set_ylim(phi2mm(ax2.get_ylim()[0]),phi2mm(ax2.get_ylim()[1]))
ax2_mm.set_ylabel('D84 grainsize mm')
plt.gca().invert_xaxis()

# D90 plot
ax3 = plt.subplot(4,1,3)
plt.plot(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'],sand_a['D90 Phi'],'k.')
mask = ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'])) & ~np.isnan(np.array(sand_a['D90 Phi']))
d90_regress = linregress(sand_a['Distance along profile [m]'][mask],sand_a['D90 Phi'][mask])
x = np.linspace(0,400,401)
ax3.plot(x, d90_regress[0]*x + d90_regress[1],'k--')
ax3.annotate('$r^2 = %.2f$' %d90_regress[2]**2, xy=(0.85,0.9), xycoords="axes fraction")
ax3.set_xlim(0,400)
ax3.set_ylabel('D90 grainsize $\phi$')
plt.grid()
ax3_mm = ax3.twinx()
ax3_mm.set_ylim(phi2mm(ax3.get_ylim()[0]),phi2mm(ax3.get_ylim()[1]))
ax3_mm.set_ylabel('D90 grainsize mm')
plt.gca().invert_xaxis()

# Topography plot
ax4 = plt.subplot(4,1,4)
plt.plot(topo_data['Distance frome shore [m]'],topo_data['Elevation [m]'],'k-')
core_locs = plt.plot(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'],core_data['Elevation [m]'],'ro')
for i in range(0, np.size(core_data['Name'])):
    ax4.annotate(core_data['Name'][i],xy=(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'][i]-3,core_data['Elevation [m]'][i]+8),

## Plot g.s. distributions, map color of lines to distance inland

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8.5,11))

# g.s. distributions plot
ax1 = plt.subplot(2,1,1)
phibins = np.array(sand_a.columns[6:70])
gs_dist = np.array(sand_a.iloc[:,6:70])
cmap = mpl.cm.viridis
norm = mpl.colors.Normalize(vmin=np.min(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]']),
                            vmax=np.max(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]']))
scalarMap = mpl.cm.ScalarMappable(norm=norm, cmap=cmap)
for i in range(0, np.shape(gs_dist)[0]):
    colorVal = scalarMap.to_rgba(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'][i])
    plt.plot(phibins, gs_dist[i],'-', color = colorVal)
ax1.set_ylabel('weight %')
ax1.set_xlabel('grainsize [$\phi$]')
ax1_mm = ax1.twiny()
ax1_mm.set_xscale('log')
ax1_mm.set_xlim(phi2mm(ax1.get_xlim()[0]),phi2mm(ax1.get_xlim()[1]))
ax1_mm.set_xlabel('grainsize [mm]')

cb_ax = fig.add_axes([0.92,0.55,0.01,0.35])
cb = mpl.colorbar.ColorbarBase(cb_ax, cmap=cmap,
                                norm=norm,
                                orientation='vertical')
cb.set_label('Distance from shoreline [m]')
# Topography plot
ax2 = plt.subplot(2,1,2)
plt.plot(topo_data['Distance frome shore [m]'],topo_data['Elevation [m]'],'k-')
for i in range(0, np.size(core_data['Name'])):
    colorVal = scalarMap.to_rgba(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'][i])
    plt.plot(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'][i],core_data['Elevation [m]'][i],'o',mfc = colorVal)
    ax2.annotate(core_data['Name'][i],xy=(core_data['Distance frome shore [m]'][i]+3,core_data['Elevation [m]'][i]+4),
                rotation=90)
ax2.set_xlim(0,400)
ax2.set_ylabel('Elevation [m]')
ax2.set_xlabel('Distance from shoreline [m]')
plt.grid()
plt.gca().invert_xaxis()

plt.suptitle('Sand A', fontsize=20)
